Itâ€™ll make the contrast very intuitive â€” especially how system calls and services flow differently.



Excellent ðŸ‘Œ â€” letâ€™s visualize **Docker vs. MKRL** execution stacks for your **Flask app on RHEL base image** in a clear side-by-side diagram (text-based schematic).

